docs.lead_paragraph: Doris Day has not made a movie since 1968--her last, no landmark, was "With Six You Get Eggroll"--but her image is indelible. As Oscar Levant said, "I knew Doris Day before she was a virgin." She quotes that, self-mockingly, in her book "Doris Day: Her Own Story" (her story, but written by A.E. Hotchner).
